Web page where users can choose a picture on the site and color it away with the colors of their choice. This is a place for users from any age to relax and express their imagination and creativity through beloved Disney characters.

Q: How are you able to get an MSCS ?

A: Northeastern University has a program called Align that helps students transitioning careers have a years worth of intensive CS classes prior to moving onto the Master courses

Q: Why did you choose to transition careers ?

A: What interested me about both Medicine and Engineering is I wanted to know how the object or body worked, what made them tick, how to debug a health issue or coding question, and how to make them more efficient

Q: What areas are you interested in?

A: Im interested in backend positions, frontend positions, and full stack positions
